snippet.title: Qinoto PAX East Trailer
snippet.description: Fold the world to find your identity in Qinoto, the award winning Folding storybook puzzle game. Help Qinoto the little fox discover the truth about herself as you crease and fold the world like paper to uncover hidden secrets and mysteries.
